<section class="py-20 md:py-24 bg-[#1e4a30] text-center">
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[3.2rem] font-heading text-white leading-tight mb-4">Planning an Event?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/80 max-w-[600px] mx-auto text-[1.1rem] mb-8">We offer catering services for all types of events. Let us bring the authentic flavors of Kerala to your special occasion.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-7 py-3 rounded-full font-medium text-base transition-all duration-300 border-2 border-transparent bg-[#c75438] text-white shadow-md hover:bg-[#b0462e] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-lg">Inquire About Catering</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#faf8f5] border-y border-black/5">
    <div class="w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
        <div class="text-center mb-12 reveal">
            <span class="inline-block text-[#c75438] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[2px] text-[0.85rem] mb-3">Testimonials</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[3.2rem] font-heading text-[#1e4a30] leading-tight mb-6">What Our Customers Say</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-[#f1ebd9] p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm reveal border border-[#dca43b]/10">
                <div class="text-[#dca43b] mb-4 text-xl tracking-widest">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="italic text-gray-500 mb-6 text-lg">"We ordered biryani for 25 people, and overall, the experience was great. The food was flavorful and well-prepared, and everyone enjoyed it. Would definitely consider ordering again!"</p>
                <h4 class="text-[#1e4a30] font-heading font-semibold text-lg">- Basil Paul</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#f1ebd9] p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-sm reveal delay-1 border border-[#dca43b]/10">
                <div class="text-[#dca43b] mb-4 text-xl tracking-widest">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="italic text-gray-500 mb-6 text-lg">"Customer friendly staff and tasty food. Order a takeaway Chilli-pork with Paratha. Very nice packing. The food was so delicious. People who love spicy food can try this. Enjoyed."</p>
                <h4 class="text-[#1e4a30] font-heading font-semibold text-lg">- Denn P</h4>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

