                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-[3.2rem] font-heading text-[#1e4a30] leading-tight mb-6">Visit Our Kitchen</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[1.1rem] mb-10">Experience our warm ambiance or grab a quick takeaway. We are always happy to serve you.</p>
                
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 lg:gap-8">
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-[#1e4a30] font-heading text-xl mb-2">📍 Location</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">147/149 Ohaupo Road,<br>Melville, Hamilton 3206</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-[#1e4a30] font-heading text-xl mb-2">📞 Contact</h4>
                        <p><a href="tel:078430307" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-[#c75438] transition-colors">+64 07 843 0307</a></p>
                        <p><a href="tel:02108397130" class="text-gray-700 hover:text-[#c75438] transition-colors">+64 21 0839 7130 (Jinil)</a></p>
                    </div>
