                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4 class="text-[#1e4a30] font-heading text-xl mb-2">🕒 Hours of Operation</h4>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Open 7 Days a week<br>11:00 AM – 9:00 PM</p>
                    </div>
